Shard\" title=\"Moon Shard\"><img alt=\"Moon Shard.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Moon_Shard.png?50cae4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>5</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookie_Cutter_Shell\" title=\"Cookie Cutter Shell\"><img alt=\"Cookie Cutter Shell.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cookie_Cutter_Shell.png?74cfd4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>5</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crabby_Hermit\" title=\"Crabby Hermit\"><img alt=\"Crabby Hermit.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crabby_Hermit.png/42px-Crabby_Hermit.png?ffb833\" width=\"42\" height=\"62\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Combriner\" title=\"Combriner\"><img alt=\"Combriner.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Combriner.png?4f963e\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Moon_Rock_outdated.png\" class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Moon_Rock_outdated.png?63bb11\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" class=\"thumbimage\"></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Moon_Rock_outdated.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Old Moon Rock icon.</div></div></div>\n<ul><li>Moon Rocks are considered to be part of <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/A_New_Reign\" title=\"A New Reign\">A New Reign</a></i>, even though they were introduced before the official start of the beta branch in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together/Version_History#November_5,_2014_-_...In_with_the_New\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together/Version History\">...In with the New</a></i> update.</li>\n<li>In the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/A_New_Reign#September_1,_2016_-_A_Little_Fixer_Upper\" title=\"A New Reign\">A Little Fixer Upper</a></i> update, the textures for Moon Rocks and all related items were updated.</li>\n<li>Even though Moon Rocks are not available in the singleplayer game, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Characters\" title=\"Characters\">Characters</a> introduced with the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Hamlet\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Hamlet\">Hamlet</a></i> DLC have unused examination quotes for them.</li></ul>\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Mining_Moon_Rocks.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Several Moon Rocks next to a Meteor Boulder.\"><img alt=\"Several Moon Rocks next to a Meteor Boulder.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Mining_Moon_Rocks.png/120px-Mining_Moon_Rocks.png?ea81ee\" width=\"120\" height=\"97\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Several Moon Rocks next to a Meteor Boulder.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Moon_Rock_Walls.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Old Moon Rock texture items beside some Moon Rock Walls.\"><img alt=\"Old Moon Rock texture items beside some Moon Rock Walls.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Moon_Rock_Walls.png/120px-Moon_Rock_Walls.png?a8b568\" width=\"120\" height=\"90\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Old Moon Rock texture items beside some Moon Rock Walls.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Early_Moon_Rock.jpg\" class=\"image\" title=\"An early texture for the Moon Rock as shown in the &quot;...In With The New&quot; update trailer.\"><img alt=\"An early texture for the Moon Rock as shown in the &quot;...In With The New&quot; update trailer.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Early_Moon_Rock.jpg/120px-Early_Moon_Rock.jpg?ddf211\" width=\"120\" height=\"101\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">An early texture for the Moon Rock as shown in the &quot;...In With The New&quot; update trailer.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Resources-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moon_Rock#Resources-0\">Resources</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Craftable_Items-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moon_Rock#Craftable_Items-0\">Craftable Items</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"Food-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moon_Rock#Food-0\">Food</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moon_Rock#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Moon_Rock#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
